                  <p>Personal data processing by OFeX is always carried out in a legal and fair manner. OFeX will only process personal data for particular, pre-determined purposes that are or were legitimate with regard to applicable law and that are relevant to OFeX’s business. You will always know what kind of information you provide to OFeX after reading our privacy policy.</p>
                  <p>OFeX uses personal data for the following purposes:
                      <ul style=" margin-left: 2%">

                        <li>To provide and deliver products and services </li>
                        <li>To communicate with you and respond to your inquiries or requests </li>
                        <li>To establish and maintain business relationships </li>
                        <li>To fulfill contractual obligations, including processing orders, deliveries, and billing </li>
                        <li>To ensure the performance and quality of our products and services </li>
                        <li>To improve our products, services, and customer experience </li>
